page.title: 21OMG I can't believe I've found my contrabution to the Domesday Project
page.content:
OMG I can't believe I've found my contribution to the Domesday Project.

I remember spending ages writing my story and drawing a picture at the top page showing me playing "Murder Ball" - A good piece of creative writing, and much better than my wife's contribution which can be found under Walderslade in Kent, which consists of a survey taken at the local shops. She does however, have a picture showing her taking the survey; she's the one on the far right in the red dress!
Matthew Down
